Jean-Michel Basquiat x Chuck Taylor All Star High TD 'Pez Dispenser'
results.story: The Jean-Michel Basquiat x Converse Chuck Taylor All Star High TD ‘Pez Dispenser’ is taken from a capsule collection celebrating the legacy of the influential Brooklyn-born artist. His Pez Dispenser graphic is appliqued on the lateral side of the upper, crafted from black canvas and lined in breathable mesh. A circular All Star patch adorns the medial ankle, while ‘Basquiat’ is inscribed across the tongue. The high-top rides on a crisp white rubber midsole with contrasting black pinstripes.

Space Jam x Chuck Taylor All Star High TD 'Tune Squad'
results.story: The Converse Chuck Taylor All Star High TD ‘Tune Squad’ pays tribute to LeBron James’ animated teammates from ‘Space Jam: A New Legacy.’ The black canvas upper is covered in a tonal circuit board print and colorful graphics that depict a cast of Looney Tunes all-stars, including Bugs Bunny, Lola Bunny, Daffy Duck, Marvin the Martian, and Taz. Orange accents make their way to the circular All Star ankle patch and tongue, featuring Tune Squad branding. The high-top sits on a crisp white rubber midsole with contrasting black pinstripes.

results.name: Space Jam x Chuck Taylor All Star High TD 'Tune Squad'
results.story: The Converse Chuck Taylor All Star High TD ‘Tune Squad’ celebrates the release of ‘Space Jam: A New Legacy’ with a scaled-down build made for little feet. The black canvas upper features a tonal circuit board print and colorful graphics made up of the film’s animated cast, including Bugs Bunny, Lola Bunny, Daffy Duck, Tweety Bird, Marvin the Martian, Taz and more. Tune Squad branding graces the tongue, while a circular All Star patch adorns the medial ankle. The high-top rests on a crisp white rubber midsole with contrasting black pinstripes.

results.name: Space Jam x Chuck 70 High TD 'A New Legacy'
results.story: Celebrating the release of LeBron James’ standalone ‘Space Jam’ sequel, the Converse Chuck 70 High TD ‘A New Legacy’ makes use of a black canvas upper with wraparound orange and yellow rings inspired by classic Looney Tunes branding. Atop the lateral heel, mismatched and oversized chenille patches feature the Tune Squad logo on the left shoe and LeBron James’ Tune Squad jersey number on the right. The high-top rides on an off-white rubber midsole with contrasting black pinstripes.

Chuck Taylor All Star Low TD 'Allover Metallic Stars - White'
results.story: Built for toddlers, the Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Low TD ‘Allover Metallic Stars’ features convenient slip-on construction with dual hook-and-loop closure in lieu of conventional laces. The white canvas upper is covered in all-over print made up of multicolor stars in a metallic tint. A webbing pull tab at the heel assists with easy on and off, while a SmartFOAM sockliner delivers cushioned comfort for growing feet. Traditional Chuck details include a reinforced toe cap and a woven Converse All Star tag atop the tongue.

Chuck Taylor All Star Ox TD 'Optic White'
results.story: The Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Ox TD is characterized by distinctly retro styling and court-specific tooling. Debuted in December 2018, this version for kid's is clad in Optic White canvas reinforced by metal eyelets and a signature toe cap. A classic tricolor palette revamps the tongue label, foxing bands and heel patch. The sneaker is supported by a vulcanized rubber sole equipping Waffle tread.

results.name: Chuck Taylor All Star Hi TD 'Oxygen Blue'
results.story: The Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Hi TD distills nostalgia and classic style for kids. Released in December 2018, this edition's Oxygen Blue canvas upper is detailed with contrast topstitching and the iconic All-Star ankle patch. A toe cap, metal eyelets and high foxing tape reinforce the construction for added durability. Featuring a sidewall stripe and heel logo, the sneaker's vulcanized rubber outsole includes Waffle tread.

results.name: Chuck Taylor All Star Ox 'Cosmos Pink'
results.story: The Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Ox sneaker is a playful rework of the icon just for kids. Debuted in December 2018, this edition takes a bold stance in Cosmos Pink canvas offset by a white toe cap and topstitching. Metal eyelets promote durability and signature logo patches hallmark the update. Reinforced by contrast foxing tape and a corrugated bumper, the vulcanized rubber sole resists abrasion thanks to classic Waffle tread.

Chuck Taylor All Star Ox TD 'Kombu'
results.story: Converse's Chuck Taylor All Star Ox TD is a laid-back rendition of the celebrated sneaker icon. This kid's version—arrived in December 2018—captures the classic canvas upper in 'Kombu' with a white toe cap, contrast stitching and metal eyelets. All-Star patches are emblazoned on the tongue and heel. Its vulcanized rubber outsole comes with high foxing tape and a split-colored Waffle tread for durability.

results.name: Chuck Taylor All Star Ox 'Roadtrip Blue'
results.story: Converse's Chuck Taylor All Star Ox sneaker recalls the hoops icon in a low-cut profile infused with classic elements. Updated in December 2018, this kid's version comes in Roadtrip Blue canvas finished with contrast topstitching, a white toe cap and gold-tone metal eyelets. Signature logo patches appear on the tongue and heel. Its vulcanized rubber sole is reinforced by a high foxing rim and Waffle grip.

Chuck Taylor All Star Street Hi 'Thunder'
results.story: Converse's Chuck Taylor All Star Street Hi sneaker for kids sits between sport heritage and modern style. Released in December 2018, this Thunder edition is given a split-colored leather upper contrasted by bright lining, a cap toe and single-wrapped foxing tape. Classic branding includes a star on the tongue, All-Star ankle patch and logo to the heel. Its vulcanized rubber sole offers a surefooted step thanks to Waffle tread.

Chuck Taylor All Star Ox 'Pink Paper'
results.story: Converse's Chuck Taylor All Star Ox sneaker pairs old-school elements and modern construction. This kid's variant—delivered in December 2018—flaunts a canvas upper in a playful Pink Paper hue, toe cap for durability and polished metal eyelets. Signature branding is echoed on tongue and heel. Contrasted by high foxing tape and a sidewall stripe, the vulcanized white rubber sole employs gum Waffle tread for stability.

results.name: Chuck Taylor All Star Ox 'Aegean Aqua'
results.story: The Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Ox kid's sneaker is classic and versatile, sporting heritage-inspired elements that made the original an icon. Delivered in December 2018, this Aegean Aqua update has a topstitched canvas upper, metal eyelets and a rubberized toe cap for added protection. Dual-toned patch logos brand the tongue and heel. Its vulcanized outsole is accompanied by a corrugated bumper and grippy Waffle tread.

results.name: Chuck Taylor All Star Ox TD 'Navy'
results.story: The Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Ox T sneaker is the court icon scaled down in size for kids. Updated in December 2018, this version is constructed of navy canvas and detailed with a signature toe cap, contrast stitching and metal eyelets. Two-tone branding is placed on the tongue and heel for classic style. Its vulcanized rubber sole is completed with a corrugated bumper and Waffle-patterned gum tread.

results.name: Chuck Taylor All Star 2V Low Infant 'Charcoal Grey'
Chuck Taylor All Star Ox 'Atomic Blue'
results.story: The Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Ox is the court icon redesigned for the playground. Launched in December 2018, this kid's iteration in Atomic Blue canvas is contrasted by a bright hue for the laces and stitching. Polished metal eyelets, a signature toe cap and foxing tape offer durability and add classic style. The sneaker is set on top of a vulcanized rubber sole utilizing a Waffle tread pattern for traction.

results.name: Chuck Taylor All Star Ox 'Obsidian'
results.story: Converse's Chuck Taylor All Star Ox matches modern and heritage design elements in a supportive profile to help little ones build mobility. Updated in December 2018, this kid's variant arrives in Obsidian canvas featuring dotted laces, a contrast toe cap and tonal metal eyelets. Dual-tone patches embellish the tongue and heel. The sneaker owes its durability to high foxing tape and Waffle grip on the striped, vulcanized rubber sole.

results.name: Hello Kitty x One Star Low Top Velcro TD 'Red'
results.story: Hello Kitty teamed up with Converse to release a velcro version of the One Star silhouette. The Hello Kitty x One Star Low Top Velcro TD 'Red' features a red suede upper with a padded collar for comfort, matching polka dot lining, and two velcro straps on the midfoot. The low top also boasts an oversized tongue tab, a chunky white midsole, and a vulcanized outsole for added traction.

results.name: Hello Kitty x Chuck Taylor All Star Ox TD 'Red'
results.story: Converse joined forces with Hello Kitty to release a toddler-sized iteration of the low cut Chuck Taylor. The Hello Kitty x Chuck Taylor All Star TD 'Red' features a red canvas upper with Hello Kitty and Chuck Taylor faces in red and blue. The sneaker also boasts a white rubber toe cap, a branded tongue patch, and a low cut construction for a broader range of motion.

results.name: Hello Kitty x Chuck Taylor All Star Hi TD 'Black Blue'
results.story: Released exclusively in grade school sizing, the Hello Kitty x Chuck Taylor All Star High Top GS 'Black Blue' features a black canvas upper with white stars outlined throughout. The sneaker also boasts a white rubber toe cap, a vulcanized outsole for traction, and a large Hello Kitty graphic on the heel side.

results.name: Hello Kitty x Chuck Taylor All Star Ox TD 'White'
results.story: Released in sizes for the whole family, this toddler’s version of the Hello Kitty x Chuck Taylor All Star 'White' debuted as part of a collaboration between Converse and Sanrio in 2018. The low-top design is clad in white canvas with an iconic pattern depicting Hello Kitty, fruit, and cupcakes. The collaborative look is complemented by the same stylized fruit on the shoe’s classic white rubber sole.

results.name: Hello Kitty x Chuck Taylor All Star Canvas Hi TD 'White'
results.story: Pop culture icon Hello Kitty partnered with Converse to release a toddlers’ shoe that celebrates friendship. The Hello Kitty x Chuck Taylor All Star Canvas High Top TD was designed in the mold of the classic Chuck Taylor silhouette, with a white canvas upper and red accents on the midsole lining. The high-top also boasts graphics of Hello Kitty and her friends along the sides and a large Hello Kitty head on the tongue.

results.name: Hello Kitty x Chuck Taylor Canvas Low Top TD
results.story: Converse released this toddler-sized colorway as part of a collaboration with Hello Kitty. The Hello Kitty x Chuck Taylor Canvas Low Top TD features a breathable black canvas upper with Hello Kitty and friends graphics throughout. The sneaker also boasts a rubber toe cap, a branded tongue and red “Say hello to me when you see me” lettering on the white midsole.

results.story: The classic Converse sneaker takes on a mini-version for growing steps with the CT All Star Toddler Ox. Mimicking the adult version, the shoe is armed with a black canvas upper and contrasting white stitching surrounding the ankle and along the vamp. Four metal eyelets are all it takes to lace up the small shoe with traditional cotton laces. A rubber toe, midfoot and outsole protect the foot and deliver comfort for increasing strides.
